characterCustomizations.biography:
I am the GM of Heroes of Time. Heroes of Time is always recruiting.
We have every AOTC since the beginning of Legion and we do a lot of keys from low to high together.
We are looking for people who like to raid, do keys, pvp and other events. We are not hardcore but neither are we just a "social" guild. We are somewhere in between. We often help people gear up so they can raid with us and will spend our figuring out rotations,macros or just doing research to better ourselves and our fellow guildmates. If you are looking to join a guild that has some skilled players but doesn't take itself to seriously then maybe our guild is for you.
You can get a hold of me @ Orumus#1671 on discord or Orumus#1851 on Bnet.
